IF gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 then END IF GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m=1

hotspot a, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1

IF UpCabinet=1 THEN ADD 0.02,fr_th1,low_door_h-0.01 MATERIAL gs_ShelfMat PRISM_ 5,0.02, 0,0,15, a-0.02*2,0,15, a-0.02*2,b-0.02-fr_th1,15, 0,b-0.02-fr_th1,15, 0,0,-1 DEL 1 ENDIF
unID=100 CALL "fa_gen_basecabinet" PARAMETERS a=a, b=b, zzyzx=zzyzx, gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, dob_face=dob_face, count_th=count_th, front_cab=front_cab, rear_cab=rear_cab, left_cab=left_cab, right_cab=right_cab, toe_h=toe_h, side_vis_m=side_vis_m+1, sink=0, shelf_num=shelf_num, gs_ShelfMat=gs_ShelfMat, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow, toe_mat=toe_mat, gs_cabinet_mat=gs_cabinet_mat, drawer_h=temp_drawer_h, toe_d = toe_d,gs_toe_type_m=gs_toe_type_m,fr_th1=fr_th1, basecab_unID=unID, returned_parameters unID
!!!!!****************************************** CALL DOOR PANEL door_w=a-left_cab-right_cab ADD left_cab,front_cab+fr_th1,toe_h !*** LOWER DOORS IF low_door=1 then GOSUB 20 !*** LOWER LEFT DOOR DEL 1
ADD left_cab,front_cab+fr_th1,low_door_h !*** UPPER DOORS IF up_door=1 and UpCabinet=1 then GOSUB 31 !*** UPPER LEFT DOOR DEL 1
!!!!****************************************** CALL END PANELS
IF rear_panel=1 and dob_face=0 then door_w=a-left_cab-right_cab: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD door_w+left_cab,b-rear_cab,toe_h ROTZ 180 GOSUB 40 DEL 2 ENDIF
IF left_panel then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th !*** LEFT END PANEL ADD left_cab,door_w+fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ -90 GOSUB 50 DEL 2 ENDIF
IF right_panel=1 then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD a-right_cab,fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ 90 GOSUB 50 DEL 2 ENDIF
END !! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! *** RETURN *** !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! !! !!!!!!!****************************************** LOWER DOOR 20:
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit, door_w=door_w, door_h=temp_door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_shadow=gs_shadow, doorframe_w=doorframe_w, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen,fr_th1=fr_th1, doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat, vert_gnum=vert_gnum, hor_gnum=hor_gnum, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, door_ang=door_ang, gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x=knob_pl_x,knob_pl_y=knob_pl_y, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
RETURN !!!!!!****************************************** UPPER DOOR 31:
cabdoortyp_unID=unID
CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit, door_w=door_w, door_h=up_door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_shadow=gs_shadow, doorframe_w=doorframe_w, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen,fr_th1=fr_th1, doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat, vert_gnum=vert_gnum2, hor_gnum=hor_gnum2, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, door_ang=door_ang, gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p, UpperKnob=1,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x_up=knob_pl_x_up,knob_pl_y_up=knob_pl_y_up, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
RETURN !!!!!****************************************** END PANELS 40: !! on rear panel there is no glas and grilles and knobs!! door_open=0 gs_knob_type_m=0 If iEndPanelType = 1 then gs_door_type_m=1 If iEndPanelType = 2 then gs_door_type_m=2 If iEndPanelType = 4 then gs_door_type_m=11 If iEndPanelType = 7 then gs_door_type_m=4 If iEndPanelType = 9 then gs_door_type_m=6 If iEndPanelType = 99 then gs_door_type_m=10 gs_full_edit=0
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m,gs_full_edit=0, door_w=door_w, door_h=temp_door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_shadow=gs_shadow, doorframe_w=doorframe_w_end, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, doorglas_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,knob_pl_y=low_door_h/2, gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p_end,fr_th1=0.02, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
